ActJudges Act (Removal Allowance) Order
PrecisOrder prescribing an additional period during which certain RELOCATION EXPENSES may be reimbursed to The Hon. DALLAS K. MILLER, who was required to relocate to the City of Lethbridge following his appointment as a Judge of the Court of Queen's Bench of Alberta on December 23, 2006.
